AKRIN K.K. is a Tokyo-based managed IT services company founded in 2024, providing professional data wiping services with NIST 800-88 compliance and kobutsusho kyoka licensing. We offer both on-site and off-site destruction options, comprehensive documentation, and environmentally responsible recycling for international companies operating in Japan. [Contact us](https://akrin.jp/contact) for a free assessment of your data wiping needs.

