# BLOG POST: blog-3-2-it-lifecycle-management-tokyo.md
**Publication Date:** November 17, 2025


---
title: "IT Lifecycle Management Tokyo: From Procurement to Disposal (2026 Guide)"
description: "Optimize your IT asset lifecycle in Tokyo. Learn about procurement strategies, refresh timing, TCO analysis, and Japan-specific considerations from planning through secure disposal."
keywords: ["IT lifecycle management Tokyo", "IT procurement Japan", "hardware refresh Tokyo", "IT asset disposal Japan", "TCO analysis Japan"]
