**About AKRIN**

AKRIN K.K. is a Tokyo-based managed IT services company founded in 2024, providing professional Ekahau wireless surveys for international companies operating in Japan. Our certified survey engineers conduct predictive, active, and passive surveys to design, troubleshoot, and optimize WiFi networks in Tokyo's challenging RF environment. From small offices to large enterprise deployments, we provide the data-driven analysis you need for reliable WiFi performance. [Contact us](https://akrin.jp/contact) to schedule your wireless survey.

